[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1269","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1269.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1423","title":"Sun Solaris 2.3 至 2.6 Ping 组播地址拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统中 ping 程序在处理通过回环接口（loopback interface）发送到多播地址（multicast address）的 ICMP 请求时存在缺陷，未经充分验证的输入可导致内核崩溃，引发系统 panic。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.3 至 2.6 版本（含 SunOS 5.3 至 5.6）。本地攻击者若拥有目标系统的 shell 访问权限，可通过执行 `ping -i <多播地址>` 等命令触发该拒绝服务漏洞，使系统宕机或重启。Sun Microsystems 已通过 Sun Security Bulletin 发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1423"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-06-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:24.550","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin 146 中提供的补丁程序，或升级到不受影响的 Solaris 版本。临时缓解措施：限制普通用户执行 ping 命令的权限，通过 chmod 移除 /usr/sbin/ping 的 setuid 位，或使用 RBAC 控制 ping 命令的调用，防止本地用户通过 `ping -i` 向组播地址发送请求触发系统崩溃。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319160&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319171&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319180&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319181&w=2","http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/146","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7492.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/209","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19161","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2d7ee098b36909e6f1960d9a77b8043812c482f/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1423.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1423","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1423.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2301e36f8af0694b1f220afdc97e9e07ee9e6a52/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1423.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c9v3-wqvp-m35p/GHSA-c9v3-wqvp-m35p.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000180.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5021047a-6ef5-4bd6-8286-cf4944b703c9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1423.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1269.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1385","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1385.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1192","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9116,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10799}}","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 及更早版本的 eeprom 命令存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过传递超长命令行参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码，从而将权限提升至 root。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 及更早版本，攻击者需具备本地登录权限，通过构造超长参数字符串触发栈溢出劫持控制流，最终获取 root 权限实现本地提权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1192"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-06-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:54.870","remediation":"升级 Sun Solaris 至 2.6 或 Solaris 7 及以上已修复版本（相应补丁为 103630/103630-12 等）。如无法立即升级，应限制普通用户对 eeprom 命令的执行权限（如移除 setuid 位或用 sudo 限定授权用户），并强化本地账户访问控制以缓解本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/143","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7444.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/206","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/786262dea273b0bddfc7eb6f6950f11b9f01c05c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1192.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1192","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1192.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/165075bb4c3675993ac058501ff8575bd07a9ca0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1192.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g3fh-mqxc-5774/GHSA-g3fh-mqxc-5774.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000179.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8a8af7e4-8516-4c12-b569-28cea0f3e94e.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1192.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1385.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1281","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1281.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1483","title":"svgalib zgv 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"svgalib 1.2.10 及更早版本中的 zgv 图形查看器存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序在处理 HOME 环境变量时未对输入长度进行有效边界检查，本地攻击者可通过设置超长的 HOME 环境变量值触发栈溢出，进而覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响使用 svgalib 进行图形显示的系统环境，攻击需具备本地登录权限，成功利用后可能导致以 zgv 运行用户权限执行恶意代码，进而获取对系统的未授权控制。建议用户及时升级 svgalib 至修复版本，或避免在不受信任的环境中运行 zgv。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1483"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-06-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:32.297","remediation":"升级 svgalib 到 1.2.10 之后的版本以修复 zgv 中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如暂无法升级，可临时卸载 zgv 程序，或限制 HOME 环境变量长度不超过 1024 个字符作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/7041","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/339","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1483.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1483","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1483.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1483.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mh54-rc24-qv85/GHSA-mh54-rc24-qv85.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1483.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--cbce1835-2d70-4602-826a-02995c44b6c8.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/fd4916152066cf69446b0fbd8f7bb3a97a137e13/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1281.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1240","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1240.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0957","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9121,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10805}}","description":"MajorCool mj_key_cache 程序存在本地符号链接攻击漏洞，本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接诱导程序修改任意文件，导致权限提升或数据破坏。该漏洞要求攻击者具备本地系统访问权限，利用 mj_key_cache 处理缓存文件时未正确验证符号链接的缺陷，将目标文件重定向至敏感位置。CVSS 评分 2.1，属低危本地漏洞，影响 MajorCool 相关版本。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0957"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-06-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:24.367","remediation":"立即停止使用 MajorCool 软件，因其已长期无人维护且无安全补丁。建议迁移至现代工单系统（如 osTicket、Zammad 或 RT）。如无法立即替换，可采取临时缓解措施：确保 mj_key_cache 程序不以 root 或高权限用户运行；将临时文件目录设置为仅程序自身可写的专用目录（如 /var/cache/majorcool），避免使用 /tmp 共享临时目录；启用文件系统防篡改机制（如 Linux 的 fs.protected_symlinks=1 内核参数）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0957","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0957.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0957.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0957","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0957.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0957.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j8wr-3p25-cjqp/GHSA-j8wr-3p25-cjqp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0957.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88374/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1240.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1240.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1435","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1435.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1266","title":"UNIX rsh守护程序 用户信息泄露漏洞","description":"rsh 守护进程（rshd）在处理用户登录请求时，对有效用户名和无效用户名返回不同的错误提示信息，导致远程攻击者可通过枚举用户名的方式探测系统上的有效用户账户。该漏洞属于信息泄露类型，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，为后续暴力破解或针对性攻击提供前提条件。受影响系统包括各类运行 rshd 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1266"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-06-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:04.320","remediation":"建议立即禁用 rsh 服务（/etc/inetd.conf 注释掉 rsh 行并重启 inetd/xinetd），改用 SSH 协议替代。若必须保留 rsh，请在 /etc/hosts.allow 限制仅信任 IP 访问，并在 /etc/pam.d/rsh 添加 pam_securetty.so 防止根用户远程登录。推荐升级至 OpenSSH 8.0+ 并强制使用密钥认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/6978","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1660","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1266.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1266","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1266.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1266.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cp39-g35j-7x79/GHSA-cp39-g35j-7x79.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87775/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1266.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/andrewyang0620/Capstone-Fujitsu-1-Demo/blob/0c9014eacdeda2ea567d9f9ad3be0b262e292f1d/demo/backend/main.py","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1435.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0095","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0095.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0033","title":"Sun Solaris at 程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun 系统的 at 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于对用户输入数据长度校验不严，本地攻击者可向 at 程序提交特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 SunOS、UnixWare、Open Desktop、OpenServer 等多个 Unix 操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。仅需本地账户即可利用，无需认证。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0033"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-06-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.453","remediation":"立即升级 Sun Solaris 至 2.5.1 及以上安全补丁版本，或安装 Sun 发布的对应安全补丁（如 105830-xx 系列）。对于 UnixWare/OpenServer 等受影响系统，升级至厂商修复版本。临时缓解措施：移除 at 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/at），或通过编辑 cron.allow/at.allow 文件严格限制可执行 at 命令的用户白名单。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0033"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0095.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0197","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0197.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0083","title":"SGI IRIX FTP 文件描述符泄露漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统的 FTP 服务中存在文件描述符泄露漏洞，`getcwd()` 函数在处理 FTP 请求时未能正确关闭文件描述符，导致系统文件描述符资源被逐步耗尽。远程攻击者可通过多次发送特定 FTP 命令触发此漏洞，造成 FTP 服务拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0083"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.437","remediation":"建议升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.3 及以上版本（含 SGI 安全补丁 19970701-01-P），修复 FTP 守护进程 getcwd() 文件描述符泄漏问题。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 FTP 行并重启 inetd 以禁用匿名 FTP，或在网络边界防火墙封禁 TCP 21 端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0083"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0197.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0461","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0461.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0275","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 DNS Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 DNS 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标系统的 UDP 53 端口发送大量超长字符数据包，导致 DNS 服务耗尽系统资源而崩溃拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击条件简单，仅需网络可达即可实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0275"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.227","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 或更高版本安全更新，限制仅允许信任源 IP 访问 DNS 服务端口 53，在防火墙层面启用速率限制和连接数控制以缓解 DNS 泛洪攻击。建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0275","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0275.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0275","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0275.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0275.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0275.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w59j-5972-p7cr/GHSA-w59j-5972-p7cr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnt_dns_flood.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0275.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0461.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0461.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0461.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0372","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0372.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0189","title":"Sun Solaris rpcbind 服务远程未授权访问漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统中的 rpcbind 服务默认监听在 UDP 端口 111，同时会动态绑定到其他高位 UDP 端口。由于网络管理员通常仅过滤标准端口 111，而未对高位 UDP 端口实施访问控制策略，导致远程攻击者可绕过防火墙过滤规则直接访问 rpcbind 服务，进而获取系统 RPC 程序信息映射，为后续远程攻击提供信息支撑。该漏洞影响所有使用 rpcbind 的 Solaris 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0189"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:47.400","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin #142 中对应 Solaris 版本的补丁（覆盖 Solaris 2.3~2.5.1）。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制 rpcbind 仅允许 UDP 111 端口通行，并添加规则阻断高位 UDP 端口的入站流量；同时可在 /etc/system 中配置 rpcbind 仅绑定已知端口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/142"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0372.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1156","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1156.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0799","title":"BSD bootpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"bootpd 是 BOOTP（Bootstrap Protocol）协议服务器程序，2.4.3 及更早版本在处理客户端请求时，对 boot file 位置字段缺乏长度校验，当接收到包含超长路径字符串的请求时会发生缓冲区溢出。该漏洞影响使用受影响版本 bootpd 的系统，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可通过发送特制的 BOOTP 请求触发溢出，导致服务崩溃或可能执行任意代码，进而影响网络启动服务的可用性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0799"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.920","remediation":"升级 bootpd 至 2.4.4 或更高版本以修复缓冲区溢出。若无法立即升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中禁用 bootpd 服务，或通过防火墙限制仅允许受信任的 DHCP/BOOTP 客户端网段访问 67/UDP 端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0799","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0799.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0799","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0799.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0799.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cvq9-5xpv-rx24/GHSA-cvq9-5xpv-rx24.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0799.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/324/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1156.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0468","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0468.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0281","title":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 URL长路径拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 2.0 及 3.0 版本存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送超长 URL 请求，导致 IIS 服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成服务不可用。该漏洞无需身份认证即可触发，攻击门槛低，影响运行 IIS 2.0/3.0 的 Windows NT 系统。由于年代久远，微软已停止支持相关版本，建议升级至更高版本 IIS。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0281"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.960","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft IIS 4.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中启用 URL 长度限制（设置 MaxClientRequestBuffer 注册表值为 4096 字节），并在防火墙层面限制对 Web 服务 80/443 端口的异常长 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0281","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20802","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0281.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0281","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0281.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0281.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0281.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5a605876-602f-4a7d-96cb-b788c024c2a8.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0281.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0468.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0468.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0468.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0413","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0413.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0227","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 LSA/LSARPC 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的本地安全认证子系统服务（LSASS.EXE）在处理 LSA/LSARPC 请求时存在访问冲突漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求，触发 LSASS.EXE 进程崩溃，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，但无法实现远程代码执行或提权。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0227"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.290","remediation":"建议升级至受支持版本的 Windows（Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2019/2022 等），Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持且不再发布安全更新。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上阻止 TCP 135 (RPC) 和 139 (NetBIOS) 端口的入站连接，限制 LSARPC 接口的远程访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ154087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0227","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0227.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0227.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80917/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--87f50d43-aca9-4ba6-b704-6b3b4ebdaad2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d6641cf4b3c3f049679d3cd7a1e7c74ad9ced77c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0413.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0294","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0294.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0144","title":"Dan Bernstein QMail 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"QMail 1.0 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 SMTP 协议的 RCPT 命令指定大量收件人地址，导致 QMail 在处理过程中消耗过多系统资源（CPU 与内存），最终造成邮件服务瘫痪。该漏洞影响 Dan Bernstein QMail 1.0 及早期版本，CVSS 评分为 2.1，危害等级低。官方建议升级至 QMail 1.03 或更高版本进行修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0144"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.470","remediation":"升级到 netqmail 1.06 或应用 qmail-1.03 的 RCPT DoS 补丁；在 qmail-smtpd 中设置软限制参数 `MAXRCPTS`（如设为 100），限制单次 SMTP 会话的收件人数量；同时启用 `rcpthosts` 和 `morercpthosts` 控制邮件转发，防止被滥用为拒绝服务攻击的反射点。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://cr.yp.to/qmail/venema.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319024&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319029&w=2","http://www.ornl.gov/its/archives/mailing-lists/qmail/1997/06/threads.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2237","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/208","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20562","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0144","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0144.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0144.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-78g5-jc8q-wgq5/GHSA-78g5-jc8q-wgq5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2237/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0144.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0294.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0099","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0099.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0035","title":"多厂商 Unix ftpd 信号处理竞态条件漏洞","description":"ftpd 守护进程的信号处理例程中存在条件竞争漏洞（Race Condition），攻击者可利用信号处理时序差绕过文件访问控制，实现任意文件读取或写入。该漏洞影响多个 UNIX 系统中的 ftpd 实现，攻击者需与目标建立 FTP 连接并在特定操作窗口内触发竞态条件以完成利用，CVSS 评分 5.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0035"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.893","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了信号处理例程中的条件竞争问题。如无法升级，建议禁用 FTP 服务（systemctl disable vsftpd/wu-ftpd）或替换为 vsftpd/ProFTPD 等更安全的 FTP 守护进程。在不必要的情况下，可通过防火墙限制对 21 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0035"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0090","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0090.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0034","title":"Perl suidperl 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"suidperl（sperl）是 Perl 中用于执行 SUID 权限脚本的辅助程序，其在处理用户输入时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向目标系统提交特制的 Perl 脚本参数触发该溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Perl 4.x 及 5.x 版本，涉及 BSD/OS、RedHat、SGI 等多个操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0034"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.680","remediation":"升级 Perl 至 5.004 或更高版本以修复 suidperl 缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可移除 suidperl 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/suidperl），并改用 sudo 机制替代 setuid 脚本执行。长期建议彻底废弃 suidperl，使用常规 Perl 解释器配合 sudo 调用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0034","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19547","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0034","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0034.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6v5q-h64v-p5mp/GHSA-6v5q-h64v-p5mp.json","https://github.com/briandfoy/cpan-security-advisory/blob/b45d5ed44c1ca4a46a9138ebed1f2bec6deb0956/TO_DO","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0090.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0090.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0090.toml"}]